## Reimplemented Ideas (not vendored)

The quality pipeline (`references/quality/`, `scripts/lib/pack_router.py`,
`scripts/lib/quality_gate.py`, `agents/code-reviewer.md`) reimplements — in this
project's own format, not by copying files — several tool-agnostic rubrics from
[levnikolaevich/claude-code-skills](https://github.com/levnikolaevich/claude-code-skills)
(MIT):

| Idea | Upstream source |
|------|-----------------|
| Code-quality metric thresholds (complexity/size/params) | `ln-511-code-quality-checker` |
| Gated tech-debt auto-fix (≥90% confidence, low-risk only) | `ln-512-tech-debt-cleaner` |
| Three-layer dead-code detection (scan → context → entrypoint) | `ln-626-dead-code-pruning-auditor` |
| Quality-tooling bootstrap shape | `ln-740-quality-setup` |

No source files from that repository are included; only the underlying rubrics
were reimplemented.

